{
  "stem": "21437.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Of course, I wouldn't dare to-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't remember-- on top, on the beds, there, I remember just-- I don't remember the sounds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Although there was-- people were groaning and moaning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were not shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Perhaps by that time, they felt that-- that the-- that the bullets are too good for the Jews-- by that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because they knew what they're going to do anyhow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, in the third day, my father came in, and he said, quickly-- he had something like a-- a very thick-- it wasn't a sheet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like linen-- a piece of linen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was, of course, like a bag of bones-- very little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, just hop in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took me over-- like a bundle, over his shoulder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what it must have happened-- it is that somehow-- because my-- if my father would not have been there, at that time, there is no way that I would have sit here today in front of you.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they would have-- there were-- all apart from 70 people, who were somewhat useful in Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So somehow, when he came-- and with one child-- and somehow he felt-- he didn't explain to me that he felt maybe that if they will see two children, maybe I was old enough to be taken away to-- to the-- to a camp, you know?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you saying that's why he hid you and not--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't find a different reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because Lilka was certainly lighter than I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was 1/2 of my-- you know, as little as I was, she was much smaller.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the thing is that he stood there with me, over his-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --left shoulder, most of the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
